 Dolaziš.

427
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:37,800
 Brate, bio je dva puta pa par godina nije.

428
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:38,840
 To je to.

429
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:39,400
 Odlično.

430
00:35:39,580 --> 00:35:40,100
 Bogu hvala.

431
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:40,780
 Dobro, dobro.

432
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:58,260
